WEBVTT

01:38.320 --> 01:40.600
EPISODE 22

01:40.840 --> 01:43.480
After slaving away for days on end,

01:43.560 --> 01:45.120
Huantian Xidi's blacksmithing

01:45.200 --> 01:47.360
has at last made the grade.

01:47.960 --> 01:50.840
This is a joyous event
that all should celebrate!

01:51.680 --> 01:53.160
This is great!

01:53.240 --> 01:55.000
No more harsh squealing from you,

01:55.080 --> 01:58.400
and no more being summoned
to help you advance the grade.

02:00.680 --> 02:05.000
Um, the sword I'm making
is still missing a material.

02:05.680 --> 02:07.520
I can't beat the boss.

02:07.600 --> 02:09.280
Weiwei.

02:09.479 --> 02:12.480
Take pity after the emotional trauma
I suffered today.

02:13.960 --> 02:14.960
Get the laptop.

02:34.840 --> 02:36.920
You collect it, Weiwei.

02:38.400 --> 02:40.920
Drop a material...

02:45.080 --> 02:48.000
Weiwei, you should go
buy a lottery ticket!

02:48.080 --> 02:49.720
You got it at the first try!

02:50.440 --> 02:52.200
Now you have all the materials you need.

02:52.280 --> 02:54.200
- Go to the blacksmith again.
- Okay.

02:55.520 --> 02:58.440
It's time to witness history being made.
Watch this!

03:07.840 --> 03:08.800
Weiwei?

03:10.040 --> 03:12.560
- What is it?
- I'm nervous.

03:13.280 --> 03:16.080
Now I use a purple ambrosia vase
to reforge the property.

03:16.280 --> 03:19.000
It's all about luck and results now.

03:29.160 --> 03:31.680
Weiwei, why don't you click it for me?

03:33.800 --> 03:36.760
It's not a good idea.
It's a gift for you friend.

03:36.840 --> 03:40.560
I shouldn't be the one
to take this critical step.

03:42.120 --> 03:45.520
Look at my finger. It's still scarred.

03:45.600 --> 03:47.280
What if I click on it,

03:47.840 --> 03:50.520
and blood bursts out,
ruining the sword and my life?

03:51.000 --> 03:53.480
Anyway, you're clearly lucky tonight.

03:53.560 --> 03:55.760
Such a rare material dropped for you
at the first try!

03:57.520 --> 03:58.880
Well...

04:04.160 --> 04:07.080
- I'll click on it now?
- Yes.

04:18.560 --> 04:21.360
Erxi... It's the highest grade sword!

04:22.120 --> 04:24.400
Goodness! I'm the luckiest girl!

04:24.480 --> 04:27.680
Weiwei, what would I ever do without you?

04:27.760 --> 04:29.760
Chill out. Okay.

04:29.840 --> 04:33.160
Now you can engrave the sword
and make your feelings known.

04:33.240 --> 04:34.200
Go ahead.

04:38.880 --> 04:44.080
- Weiwei, it's a bit personal, can you...
- Got it.

04:44.520 --> 04:45.960
I see nothing.

04:59.320 --> 05:02.600
Your Highness, are you done?

05:04.000 --> 05:05.480
Let me admire it some more.

05:16.160 --> 05:19.120
- Hello?
- Weiwei, this is Diemeng.

05:19.560 --> 05:21.040
- Diemeng?
- Yes.

05:21.400 --> 05:24.200
Are you free tomorrow? Let's have dinner.

05:24.920 --> 05:28.440
- Tomorrow?
- Are you free?

05:28.960 --> 05:29.800
I think so.

05:30.800 --> 05:32.040
That's great!

05:32.120 --> 05:34.400
I'll text you the time and address.

05:35.240 --> 05:37.240
- Sure.
- See you tomorrow.

05:37.520 --> 05:38.800
See you. Bye-bye.

05:45.880 --> 05:46.880
Someone invited you to dinner?

05:47.440 --> 05:49.040
A friend from the game.

05:49.320 --> 05:52.680
Don't you go swimming for an hour
every day with Lord?

05:52.760 --> 05:56.720
Would he mind that
you're having dinner with someone else?

05:58.200 --> 06:00.360
It doesn't matter if he minds or not.

06:00.840 --> 06:02.080
Yeah, right!

06:04.480 --> 06:05.600
What?

06:05.680 --> 06:07.800
Are you kicking away the ladder now?

06:08.720 --> 06:12.400
Weiwei, did you agree
to the dinner so fast,

06:12.480 --> 06:15.360
because you don't want to go
swimming with Lord?

06:16.280 --> 06:20.360
It must take a toll, to lose so much blood
every day from your nosebleed.

06:22.760 --> 06:26.200
- The clever die young. Get it?
- Got it.

06:27.240 --> 06:31.280
The thing is, I have to take a break
from looking at the hunk every day.

06:32.000 --> 06:35.240
- You're showing off again!
- I'm sorry.

06:35.320 --> 06:38.800
I can't help it.
I'm influenced by my surroundings.

06:39.120 --> 06:41.520
Again? Are you done?

06:41.600 --> 06:45.000
No... I'm influenced by my surroundings...

06:47.800 --> 06:49.800
Weiwei has met two friends from the game,

06:50.080 --> 06:52.920
one of them the caliber of Lord, too.

06:57.280 --> 07:01.400
I wonder what Weiguang's like.

07:14.920 --> 07:17.720
Crap... Why did I think of
that unlucky jerk?

07:18.160 --> 07:23.320
They both have "guang" in the name,
but Weiguang is the blazing sun;

07:23.960 --> 07:27.960
and Cao Guang is a two-watt light bulb,
at most.

07:36.760 --> 07:42.240
Weiguang...
when will you log on again?

08:05.040 --> 08:05.880
Here's the update!

08:06.200 --> 08:09.080
Today, Coffee's eating regularly
and pooping regularly.

08:09.160 --> 08:10.120
He's just a bit sluggish.

08:10.400 --> 08:13.600
He keeps gazing out of the window,
probably missing you.

08:43.320 --> 08:44.200
Breaking news...

08:44.280 --> 08:46.840
Coffee learned a new skill today,
catching flies.

08:47.120 --> 08:51.280
Now, you won't have to worry
about the kitty being bored.

08:52.160 --> 08:56.280
So, I opened all the windows in the house
to welcome the flies.

08:56.360 --> 08:58.560
I hope you won't mind.

09:02.960 --> 09:04.680
Coffee is cute,

09:04.840 --> 09:09.480
but someone's big face
ruined the composition.

09:34.520 --> 09:36.000
Coffee's off-screen line is,

09:36.360 --> 09:40.120
"Dissing Ms. Erxi is dissing on me.

09:40.200 --> 09:42.280
I sneer at you!"

09:55.600 --> 09:56.640
Let's sit there.

09:58.200 --> 09:59.040
Okay.

10:04.680 --> 10:06.800
Hi, there. Who will be ordering?

10:08.480 --> 10:09.920
Why don't you order, Mr. K.O.?

10:11.280 --> 10:12.120
It's okay.

10:14.000 --> 10:14.840
I'll do it.

10:17.040 --> 10:18.120
Ms. Weiwei,

10:18.640 --> 10:23.040
how come you've never
addressed me as Mr. Hao?

10:25.640 --> 10:29.160
If I called you that, Lord would off me.

10:31.040 --> 10:35.960
- Why's that?
- Mr. Hao, hao means "more"...

10:36.800 --> 10:38.960
- Mr. More.
- Mr. More.

10:39.040 --> 10:39.960
Forget it...

10:41.040 --> 10:42.920
Don't call me that. If you do,

10:43.000 --> 10:44.920
Lord won't off you, he'll just off me.

10:45.600 --> 10:48.160
Phew! I nearly kissed my life goodbye.

10:49.360 --> 10:52.600
I'll order... to console my fragile heart.

11:01.240 --> 11:02.280
Have you noticed?

11:02.360 --> 11:06.200
Since Mrs. Nai's been around,
Nai has become so pampered.

11:06.280 --> 11:07.720
When he was too busy to eat lunch,

11:07.800 --> 11:09.040
he'd just eat buns with water.

11:09.240 --> 11:11.680
Now, he's got everything.

11:11.760 --> 11:14.800
- So pampered.
- He'd only eat buns and water?

11:14.960 --> 11:17.440
You have no idea.
Sometimes, he'd even skip the buns.

11:20.240 --> 11:22.120
Look at how it pains her!

11:23.120 --> 11:26.560
I've also noticed,
he's not very picky with food.

11:26.720 --> 11:28.720
He asked me to bring him fried rice!

11:28.960 --> 11:30.600
That's not nutritious enough.

11:31.240 --> 11:33.720
I'll handle his nutritionally
balanced diet now.

11:34.720 --> 11:38.400
Paired with a juice from the heart,
he'll have food and drink.

11:39.000 --> 11:41.480
It's 100 percent nutritionally balanced.

11:42.200 --> 11:44.600
Help! All this showing off
is making me gag.

11:46.760 --> 11:48.160
Back in the day,

11:48.240 --> 11:51.480
I had a serious internet romance
right in front of me,

11:51.680 --> 11:53.480
but I took it for granted.

11:53.960 --> 11:57.560
Thinking back on it now,
I could really kick myself.

11:58.560 --> 12:01.280
Mr. Hao, internet romance
isn't the way to go.

12:02.920 --> 12:04.160
What about you and Xiao Nai?

12:06.400 --> 12:10.840
We met online, got to know each other
in real life, then...

12:11.760 --> 12:13.160
Who was it with? Do tell!

12:15.320 --> 12:18.360
That relationship wasn't in
"A Chinese Ghost Story."

12:18.760 --> 12:20.480
Before I got into "A Chinese Ghost Story,"

12:20.560 --> 12:23.280
I played a game called "Fantasy Planet."

12:24.120 --> 12:25.520
My avatar was a celestial doctor.

12:26.240 --> 12:28.160
I know the game!

12:28.560 --> 12:31.960
Only girls choose the celestial doctor.
You used the female avatar?

12:32.040 --> 12:34.440
That's right. At the time,

12:34.520 --> 12:36.680
that was the only character
up to my aesthetic standards.

12:37.480 --> 12:39.880
Then, many of my friends
became in-game spouses.

12:40.320 --> 12:42.240
I thought, I want one, too.

12:43.200 --> 12:45.920
In-game spouses tend to be
the opposite sex.

12:46.000 --> 12:49.480
You had a female avatar,
so you were looking for a male player?

12:49.560 --> 12:52.520
Wrong! I was looking for
a bio-woman in disguise.

12:55.640 --> 12:57.840
- It works that way?
- Of course!

12:58.040 --> 13:01.840
There's a male avatar in the game
called Huajian,

13:02.920 --> 13:04.760
whose character design is very feminine.

13:05.040 --> 13:07.040
Most boys wouldn't pick it.

13:07.840 --> 13:09.920
Instead, it was popular with girls.

13:10.080 --> 13:12.720
So, I thought, I'll look for a Huajian.

13:13.080 --> 13:16.160
I even took pains to find
a player with a poetic name,

13:16.240 --> 13:17.720
one that was obviously a girl.

13:18.080 --> 13:21.720
The handle was... Shoukezhai Xingchen,
meaning "within reach of stars."

13:24.240 --> 13:27.480
The name's very confident and bold.

13:27.560 --> 13:28.480
Why did you think it must be a girl?

13:29.440 --> 13:31.920
Well... I just thought,

13:32.000 --> 13:34.200
only girls would want to pluck stars.

13:35.160 --> 13:37.640
In order to show I'm a deep person,

13:37.720 --> 13:40.040
I chose not to ask the gender question.

13:40.120 --> 13:45.880
Turns out,
it was a man disguised as a bio-woman,

13:46.720 --> 13:49.160
So complicated!
Was it a man or a woman?

13:50.080 --> 13:51.680
He was all man.

13:52.520 --> 13:55.720
- What happened after that?
- There's no after.

13:56.160 --> 13:57.840
As soon as I found out he's a guy,

13:58.120 --> 14:00.600
I... Never touched that game again.

14:02.120 --> 14:05.320
Mr. Girly, how dare you criticize him?

14:05.400 --> 14:07.600
You pretended to be a girl player,

14:07.680 --> 14:10.320
led him on, then dumped him.

14:10.760 --> 14:11.760
Heartbreaker!

14:12.920 --> 14:14.640
I'm not a heartbreaker, I...

14:14.960 --> 14:17.400
At first, my motive was very pure.

14:17.880 --> 14:20.320
Was your server called Lunar Chang'an?

14:22.880 --> 14:23.880
How did you know?

14:24.600 --> 14:26.080
Because I'm Shoukezhai Xingchen.

14:35.760 --> 14:36.600
My stomach hurts!

14:36.800 --> 14:38.840
Ms. Weiwei, hurry.
Take me to the hospital!

14:40.400 --> 14:41.360
It's that serious?

15:00.760 --> 15:03.040
The thunder and lightning was so scary!

15:03.120 --> 15:07.720
- The meeting of their gaze was intense!
- This is fate, I'm telling you.

15:09.160 --> 15:10.800
Unfortunate fate.

15:11.120 --> 15:13.480
- Weiwei...
- Yugong...

15:13.920 --> 15:15.760
- Let's go back to the office.
- Okay.

15:27.680 --> 15:30.680
Mr. Xiao, they were out of fried rice.

15:30.760 --> 15:33.640
So I packed some veggies, beef
and rice for you.

15:33.720 --> 15:34.920
I hope you won't mind.

15:36.800 --> 15:40.360
It's fine. Ms. Bei.
Please get me a glass of water.

15:42.520 --> 15:44.600
I've got it. Here.

15:46.160 --> 15:48.440
Enjoy, Lord.

15:50.920 --> 15:52.760
Why are you so attentive today?

15:55.320 --> 15:58.240
Attentiveness is in my nature.

16:04.960 --> 16:08.480
I can't have dinner with you tonight.
Diemeng invited to me to dinner.

16:08.560 --> 16:10.280
She treated me last time.
It's my turn this time.

16:10.960 --> 16:12.000
Is that so?

16:13.520 --> 16:15.400
You're not avoiding our swimming class?

16:18.400 --> 16:22.240
- You read too much into it, Mr. Xiao.
- If so, let's go tomorrow.

16:31.360 --> 16:33.120
All right, go to your dinner.

16:33.840 --> 16:35.000
It'll rain tonight, though.

16:35.520 --> 16:37.360
Don't get rained on, okay?

16:37.760 --> 16:39.000
Yes, sir.

16:39.640 --> 16:42.960
Remember to drink the juice of love
I got you. Bye.

17:32.360 --> 17:34.040
Let's go, ladies.

19:06.520 --> 19:08.600
The car's so cool!

19:09.160 --> 19:12.240
I know, right? He's so handsome, too!

19:15.760 --> 19:17.400
Hello! This way, please.

19:25.800 --> 19:30.240
So, you're Zhenshui? You must be Yaoyao?

19:30.960 --> 19:33.160
When I saw you outside,

19:33.240 --> 19:34.880
- I had no idea!
- Right?

19:34.960 --> 19:37.920
I've seen your photos,
but I didn't recognize you.

19:38.360 --> 19:40.040
You're prettier in person, Yaoyao.

19:43.680 --> 19:46.480
Okay, almost everyone's here.

19:46.840 --> 19:48.680
It's my treat today.
Order whatever you want.

19:49.720 --> 19:51.320
Server, menus please!

19:51.520 --> 19:53.480
Much obliged.

19:55.760 --> 19:57.440
Why isn't Luwei Weiwei here yet?

19:58.360 --> 20:00.400
When will she be here, Ms. Diemeng?

20:00.880 --> 20:03.480
Don't tell me, she's not coming.

20:04.960 --> 20:08.840
She's a woman of her word.
I'm sure she'll show up.

20:10.320 --> 20:11.960
We're all looking forward to it.

20:44.040 --> 20:48.480
It's such a posh place.
Did I bring enough money?

20:49.240 --> 20:52.320
Never mind, I can always call
Lord for help.

20:56.120 --> 20:57.720
Chrysanthemum Pavilion?

20:58.480 --> 21:01.600
Why does it sound like a private room?

21:04.720 --> 21:06.000
She's here.

21:06.560 --> 21:08.240
- Luwei Weiwei is here?
- Where?

21:08.320 --> 21:09.280
- Where?
- She's here?

21:09.360 --> 21:10.200
Which one?

21:10.280 --> 21:13.560
Luwei Weiwei is a beauty,
according to Ms. Diemeng.

21:14.120 --> 21:16.600
I'm so curious what she looks like.

21:16.880 --> 21:18.720
Me, too, Ms. Diemeng.

21:18.920 --> 21:20.800
Is Luwei Weiwei as pretty as Yaoyao?

21:21.840 --> 21:25.440
- You'll find out soon.
- She can't be as pretty as Yaoyao.

21:25.520 --> 21:28.320
Yaoyao is the belle of our server.

21:28.600 --> 21:30.040
Okay, don't be so excessive,

21:30.320 --> 21:33.760
- comparing me to everyone.
- Okay, I won't.

21:34.080 --> 21:36.240
Average girls aren't on the same level
as Yaoyao.

21:39.080 --> 21:42.400
If not for you, Tianxia wouldn't have
met Xiaoyu Qingqing.

21:42.480 --> 21:45.440
If not for you, me and Tianxia
wouldn't be like this today.

21:46.240 --> 21:48.600
I want you to know my pain.

21:48.680 --> 21:50.520
Let's see if you'll be laughing then.

21:52.200 --> 21:53.480
This way, miss.

22:03.200 --> 22:04.200
Here she is...

22:11.800 --> 22:14.880
Are you kidding? You call that a beauty?

22:16.640 --> 22:17.480
No way!

22:20.160 --> 22:21.040
This way, miss.

22:26.080 --> 22:27.080
She's here...

22:42.120 --> 22:43.000
What in the world?

22:58.200 --> 22:59.040
Weiwei!

23:04.360 --> 23:07.720
- I'm so glad you came to the gathering.
- Gathering?

23:09.120 --> 23:11.120
Do me this favor. I'll explain later.

23:11.760 --> 23:13.680
Here, I saved you a seat.

23:13.760 --> 23:14.960
Let's go sit down.

23:18.080 --> 23:20.880
- I did not see this coming!
- She is a beauty!

23:20.960 --> 23:22.480
I'm so surprised.

23:30.600 --> 23:34.120
- You're Luwei Weiwei?
- Yes.

23:35.520 --> 23:37.480
- So pretty.
- I know!

23:37.880 --> 23:38.720
She's a beauty indeed.

23:43.760 --> 23:46.000
Hello, everyone. I'm Luwei Weiwei.

23:47.560 --> 23:49.120
How's that possible? You're lying!

23:49.480 --> 23:51.440
You should've done your homework!

23:52.000 --> 23:54.520
We've all seen Luwei Weiwei.

23:54.600 --> 23:55.800
She looks nothing like you.

23:56.920 --> 23:58.560
You've seen Luwei Weiwei?

24:00.120 --> 24:02.880
Of course! The real Luwei Weiwei

24:02.960 --> 24:04.240
works at Zhenshui's company.

24:05.040 --> 24:06.520
Not only is she homely,

24:06.840 --> 24:08.360
she's got terrible fashion sense.

24:09.120 --> 24:12.280
She wore a plaid shirt,
like a typical geek girl.

24:12.800 --> 24:15.240
Who are you?
Why are you pretending to be Luwei Weiwei?

24:18.040 --> 24:21.600
I know!
Luwei Weiwei is afraid to meet with us.

24:21.680 --> 24:24.000
She paid you to be here, didn't she?

24:27.120 --> 24:28.520
Plaid shirt?

24:30.480 --> 24:32.600
The young master's girlfriends came today.

24:32.680 --> 24:35.920
- That was an eye-opener for me.
- Girlfriends?

24:36.200 --> 24:37.360
It's a gang of girls.

24:37.440 --> 24:38.920
They look the same and dress the same.

24:39.240 --> 24:40.520
But that's not the point.

24:40.600 --> 24:44.680
The point is, I'm an exceptional intern,

24:44.760 --> 24:47.320
yet they bossed me around like a maid.

24:47.400 --> 24:49.160
They spilled coffee on my white sneaker.

24:49.240 --> 24:53.680
I washed it all night,
but it's still stained. I want to die!

24:53.920 --> 24:57.480
So, they were the ones
who tormented Erxi. They're too much!

24:57.560 --> 24:59.560
I'll get them back for Erxi.

25:00.600 --> 25:02.720
I don't know who you're talking about.

25:03.640 --> 25:06.360
Many handles are similar
in the gaming world.

25:07.440 --> 25:10.240
Didn't you have a subaccount

25:10.320 --> 25:12.040
named Liuwai Waiwai?

25:15.160 --> 25:18.360
Plus, even if her handle
is actually Luwei Weiwei,

25:18.640 --> 25:19.680
she could be from another server.

25:19.960 --> 25:22.840
How could it be a coincidence?
You must be fake.

25:22.920 --> 25:23.800
Right?

25:24.960 --> 25:25.800
You don't believe me?

25:32.360 --> 25:33.800
Who knows if she's the real deal?

25:37.880 --> 25:39.920
Who's got a computer?

25:40.600 --> 25:42.320
- I have mine.
- Me, too.

25:42.400 --> 25:45.880
Right, we'll know for sure,
if she logs in to the game.

25:46.160 --> 25:47.880
How would we know for sure?

25:48.400 --> 25:51.120
If she's faking it,
I'm sure she'd know her account.

25:51.720 --> 25:55.600
You can fake the account,
but you can't fake maneuvering.

25:56.360 --> 25:59.160
I'll tell you what,
I'll duel the four of you.

26:00.040 --> 26:03.760
If I win all four duel matches,
will that be enough to prove

26:04.120 --> 26:05.280
I'm Luwei Weiwei?

26:05.800 --> 26:07.960
Duel? Well...

26:09.000 --> 26:10.640
What? Are you scared?

26:12.120 --> 26:14.320
Dueling is a good idea.

26:14.600 --> 26:17.600
Luwei Weiwei's maneuvering
can't be faked by just anyone.

26:17.680 --> 26:20.040
Right! Otherwise,
we don't know who to believe.

26:25.920 --> 26:28.720
Fine, let's duel! We aren't scared of you!

27:01.600 --> 27:02.440
Next!

27:29.640 --> 27:30.480
Come on.

27:39.400 --> 27:42.040
Her hands are so fast.
Her maneuvering is so smooth.

27:52.040 --> 27:53.560
Looks like you are Luwei Weiwei.

27:54.480 --> 27:57.840
It's our mistake. Let's forget the duel.

27:58.320 --> 28:00.680
We're here to meet one another. Why fight?

28:02.240 --> 28:04.680
Dueling is fun
when players meet-up like this.

28:05.760 --> 28:07.280
We agreed to four matches.

28:08.360 --> 28:10.480
What? You're scared?

28:12.760 --> 28:16.560
Let's just forget it.
I think we made a mistake.

28:16.640 --> 28:19.600
It's a gathering event.
Why get combative?

28:19.680 --> 28:21.440
Do me this favor.

28:22.240 --> 28:23.080
Who are you?

28:25.840 --> 28:26.880
I'm Zhenshui Wuxiang.

28:28.640 --> 28:29.880
It's you?

28:31.520 --> 28:35.160
Well, you can duel for her, if you want.

28:36.240 --> 28:38.120
I couldn't bully a girl.

28:39.560 --> 28:42.120
Then cut the crap. Let's get started.

29:19.120 --> 29:20.560
It's so one-sided.

29:20.640 --> 29:22.880
I know! Poor Xiaoyu Yaoyao!

29:23.320 --> 29:25.120
Luwei Weiwei is toying with her.

29:25.640 --> 29:27.920
Instead of offing her,
it's like a game of cat and mouse.

29:30.280 --> 29:33.880
Luwei Weiwei, if you want to duel,
then duel.

29:33.960 --> 29:35.280
What's the point in tormenting someone?

29:37.840 --> 29:40.240
What's the point in tormenting someone?

29:40.720 --> 29:41.800
I'm sure you would know.

29:44.160 --> 29:45.200
What do you mean?

29:45.800 --> 29:49.840
Nothing, I just got kind of tired
from the three matches.

29:50.320 --> 29:53.480
So I want to rest a bit and take it slow.

29:58.880 --> 29:59.720
Zhenshui!

30:01.240 --> 30:02.200
Zhenshui!

30:05.360 --> 30:08.080
It's just a game. Don't take it to heart.

30:09.680 --> 30:12.560
That's right, Yaoyao. It's just a game.

30:12.640 --> 30:13.960
You lose, if you're too serious.

30:19.920 --> 30:20.760
Well?

30:21.680 --> 30:24.720
Have I proved that I'm Luwei Weiwei?

30:25.320 --> 30:27.520
Yes, you have! Weiwei, you're awesome!

30:27.600 --> 30:28.920
I never saw this coming!

30:29.000 --> 30:31.200
Not only is Luwei Weiwei
not a bio-man is disguise,

30:31.360 --> 30:32.960
she's a stunner!

30:33.040 --> 30:34.480
You've been too low-key.

30:35.240 --> 30:38.880
I thought Xiaoyu Yaoyao was pretty.

30:38.960 --> 30:40.920
- Yeah.
- But once Luwei showed up,

30:41.000 --> 30:43.160
it's like Yaoyao isn't here anymore.

30:43.240 --> 30:46.080
Right? Yaoyao has faded
into the background.

30:46.520 --> 30:48.760
I'm sure there are no more doubts.

30:49.160 --> 30:51.000
We're here to meet one another,

30:51.080 --> 30:52.280
not to cast doubt on players' identities.

30:53.320 --> 30:55.960
Yaoyao and Qingqing,
you're nice girls,

30:56.040 --> 30:57.440
but you're too mistrustful.

30:58.560 --> 31:01.360
Weiwei, let's go back to our seats.
Come on, everyone.

31:02.240 --> 31:03.080
Let's go.

31:03.520 --> 31:04.760
You're amazing!

31:14.880 --> 31:15.880
Luwei...

31:17.600 --> 31:18.720
I'm Zhan Tianxia.

31:19.760 --> 31:22.880
We had some misunderstanding in the game,

31:23.160 --> 31:25.520
but since we've met today,

31:25.600 --> 31:30.400
let's let bygones be bygones.

31:30.800 --> 31:31.640
Of course.

31:33.200 --> 31:35.160
I don't need to introduce them.

31:35.240 --> 31:37.320
You already met in the dueling matches.

31:40.160 --> 31:43.240
Luwei, you're as fierce
as you are in the game.

31:45.200 --> 31:46.040
You are, too.

31:47.920 --> 31:51.120
We've all introduced ourselves.
Let's begin.

31:51.200 --> 31:54.840
Server, you can bring out the dishes now.

31:54.920 --> 31:57.840
- Add a coral grouper and two lobsters.
- Sure.

31:57.920 --> 32:00.720
- That's so expensive!
- Zhenshui, you're loaded!

32:01.280 --> 32:02.880
I want everyone to have a good time.

32:04.160 --> 32:06.600
If not for Zhenshui,
we wouldn't be dining here.

32:06.680 --> 32:08.320
Everything costs three digits, at least.

32:09.040 --> 32:11.360
Zhenshui has always been generous.

32:11.440 --> 32:13.240
He always treats everyone.

32:19.200 --> 32:21.640
Weiwei, your dress is so pretty.

32:22.160 --> 32:23.040
How much was it?

32:24.240 --> 32:26.080
I don't remember. It was a random buy.

32:29.720 --> 32:30.960
Weiwei, how should we address you?

32:32.160 --> 32:33.040
Just call me Luwei.

32:36.440 --> 32:39.840
Weiwei, I remember you're a student, too.

32:39.920 --> 32:41.000
Which school do you go to?

32:43.960 --> 32:46.720
Our school is famous for its food.

32:47.760 --> 32:50.560
"QU's prestige, BIT's food,

32:50.640 --> 32:53.240
BFSU's girls, BUAA's hunks."

32:53.680 --> 32:56.880
So, you go to BIT. What's your major?

32:57.320 --> 32:58.160
Computing.

32:59.520 --> 33:01.640
I'm a computer major at BIT, too!

33:01.720 --> 33:04.080
How come I've never see you?

33:04.680 --> 33:07.480
Crap! I was hoping to misdirect them,

33:07.560 --> 33:09.240
but this one is the real deal.

33:11.520 --> 33:14.320
Nowadays, many working women

33:14.400 --> 33:18.000
like to pretend to be college students.

33:19.400 --> 33:20.960
You're a girl.

33:21.400 --> 33:22.800
Why do you have such dirty thoughts?

33:29.080 --> 33:31.600
- Which campus are you at?
- Quanshan.

33:32.160 --> 33:34.640
You can only move to the main campus
in junior year?

33:35.320 --> 33:39.040
You're at the main campus?
No wonder I've never seen you.

33:39.120 --> 33:41.480
But you don't look older than me.

34:23.199 --> 34:24.960
How come it's always raining?

34:25.080 --> 34:27.920
Let's sing karaoke next door
and stay out of the rain.

34:28.000 --> 34:29.600
Sure, let's go.

34:30.239 --> 34:31.199
I second that.

34:31.280 --> 34:33.880
Let's drink to that. I love singing.

34:40.159 --> 34:41.719
Karaoke is a must.

34:43.159 --> 34:44.000
Hello?

34:44.679 --> 34:46.520
It's raining too hard. I'll come get you.

34:48.520 --> 34:52.239
- Okay, you can come over now.
- Sure.

35:01.840 --> 35:05.560
- Was that your boyfriend, Weiwei?
- Yes.

35:12.120 --> 35:14.080
You're leaving already, Weiwei?

35:14.160 --> 35:16.280
We're going to karaoke later.

35:16.360 --> 35:17.200
You should come!

35:17.440 --> 35:20.120
Yes, I want to hear the beauty sing.

35:20.200 --> 35:22.600
Your boyfriend should come, too.

35:22.680 --> 35:24.800
We finally met up,
and you're leaving already?

35:24.880 --> 35:27.280
- I know!
- That's true.

35:29.280 --> 35:32.600
Sorry, I can't go. I'm busy later tonight.

35:37.800 --> 35:41.680
- Check, please!
- Sure. Just a moment.

35:56.000 --> 35:57.200
It's pouring down.

35:57.280 --> 35:59.120
- How are we going to leave?
- Right?

35:59.520 --> 36:00.680
It won't stop anytime soon.

36:00.760 --> 36:04.200
- You should go. Don't stay with me.
- No way!

36:04.280 --> 36:06.360
We can't let a beauty
wait alone in the rain

36:06.640 --> 36:07.800
for her boyfriend.

36:07.880 --> 36:09.200
- That's right.
- True.

36:12.440 --> 36:14.320
He'll be here soon. It's okay.

36:14.680 --> 36:17.240
It's just karaoke.
If we sing one less song,

36:17.320 --> 36:18.920
- it won't kill us.
- Right.

36:19.000 --> 36:21.520
I think you're all just curious,

36:21.600 --> 36:23.920
what the beauty's boyfriend looks like.

36:24.560 --> 36:27.040
I'm sure I'm not the only curious one.

36:30.040 --> 36:34.080
I'd like to see
what Luwei Weiwei's boyfriend looks like.

36:35.400 --> 36:38.080
Zhenshui's handsome and rich.
His dad's company is publicly traded.

36:38.800 --> 36:41.960
I'm sure Yaoyao will win
in the boyfriend category.

37:10.560 --> 37:12.000
Here he is...

37:19.240 --> 37:20.480
It's him?

37:22.520 --> 37:24.080
- Look...
- He's dreamy!

37:29.880 --> 37:32.440
You guys have fun. I'm taking off.

37:32.680 --> 37:35.840
Weiwei, why don't you
ask your boyfriend to join us?

37:35.920 --> 37:37.520
It's a rare opportunity.

37:40.680 --> 37:44.960
No, he's an introvert.
He doesn't like strangers.

37:52.880 --> 37:53.720
Let's go.

37:58.960 --> 38:03.000
Hey! Your girlfriend has had
many in-game husbands.

38:03.080 --> 38:04.280
Did you know that?

38:14.000 --> 38:17.680
She's a home-wrecker,
always a flirt with men.

38:17.760 --> 38:22.200
Everyone here knows
she's a woman of ill repute.

38:22.280 --> 38:25.160
Handsome, don't be fooled by her.

38:26.120 --> 38:27.480
As long as she's willing to be with me,

38:29.360 --> 38:30.880
none of that matters to me.

39:03.720 --> 39:06.960
I've always known you're a master
at infuriating people,

39:07.040 --> 39:09.240
but your game face
is even more impressive.

39:09.800 --> 39:12.200
Xiaoyu Qingqing was trying to
provoke suspicion,

39:12.280 --> 39:13.120
so you'd dump me.

39:14.000 --> 39:16.200
I didn't expect you to act like,

39:16.280 --> 39:19.960
you'd never be mad at me,
even if I were unfaithful.

39:21.760 --> 39:24.080
No wonder you're Lord.

39:30.120 --> 39:35.280
Would you really be okay with it,
if I were unfaithful?

39:37.320 --> 39:38.160
Yes.

39:41.080 --> 39:43.520
I thought you'd kill the guy.

39:57.000 --> 39:57.920
Well...

39:59.360 --> 40:02.480
If you're unfaithful,
I'll restore your faith.

40:06.040 --> 40:09.360
If you lose all faith,
I'll convert you again.

40:37.640 --> 40:38.520
Coffee?

40:39.880 --> 40:40.920
Coffee?

40:41.120 --> 40:42.840
Little Coffee?

40:45.960 --> 40:49.560
Little Coffee?

40:50.560 --> 40:52.240
I knew you'd be here.

40:54.800 --> 40:57.680
It's been so long! Have you been good?

41:02.120 --> 41:05.840
Looks like someone took good care of you.

41:27.600 --> 41:30.400
A meal alone can be a good meal, too.

41:52.960 --> 41:55.080
A CHINESE GHOST STORY

42:05.600 --> 42:07.200
You're online at last, Weiguang!

42:07.400 --> 42:10.520
I'm waiting at the old place
in Jinling City. Come soon!

44:48.440 --> 44:50.880
Subtitle translation by Lu Yuhan
